{"tid":2272542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北韓中朝邊境埋地雷防武肺","createTime":"2020-11-05T06:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T06:49:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"767131022c56aa1786d5ffa5c831aea14c3ba1e0","tid":2272542,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:22:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201105/UBOMM6O3VNCU7CUDA5LKGSBTJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201105%2FUBOMM6O3VNCU7CUDA5LKGSBTJM%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4DC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=26850c19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201105%2FUBOMM6O3VNCU7CUDA5LKGSBTJM%2F&h=06b33fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201105/UBOMM6O3VNCU7CUDA5LKGSBTJM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n北韓中朝邊境埋地雷防武肺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RX4sSxN9XgE8zfHKaiU0n5_lCCw=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OKV4GBWOY5FUZE4DDDUMAJ7S5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRX4sSxN9XgE8zfHKaiU0n5_lCCw%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOKV4GBWOY5FUZE4DDDUMAJ7S5Y.jpg&h=7507a791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■北韓工人戴上口罩防疫，當局未有公佈疫情數字。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情在全球持續擴散，與中國接壤的北韓因醫療基建落後，擔心一旦爆發疫情，衞生系統無力招架。南韓情報機構稱，北韓已封鎖邊境，甚至在中朝邊境地帶埋設地雷，目的是防範疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恐疫流入 拒收外國物資<br />\n<br />\n韓國國家情報院當地時間前日發表報告，北韓於2月27日的勞動黨政治部會議文件指，一旦疫情流入北韓將大難臨頭，「死30萬還是50萬人誰都不知」，因當地防疫手段為零。<br />\n<br />\n報告又指，北韓在物資和技術均缺乏應對疫情的手段，也對疫情滿懷恐懼，規定可對防疫不力的幹部處以死刑。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n國情院稱，為防止疫情流入，北韓不接受他國包括南韓在內的物資。北韓據報有5,368宗疑似病例，其中8宗是外國人，截至10月22日，已為超過一萬名民眾進行病毒測試，至今當地仍宣稱是零確診。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，北韓把武漢肺炎確診患者關在中國邊境附近的難民營「等死」，只提供少量的食物與藥物，那些患者能否活下去，全靠家人有沒有送食物與藥物到難民營。彼得斯表示，他收到的消息是很多人不是因為武漢肺炎病死，而是餓死。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社"},{"pid":"991374ddf3981e45f1107ac02658b7e7ebe21a5c","tid":2272542,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">最有效嘅防疫措施</span>"},{"pid":"45f18bff8dfe4080ee78f36a17c6082c40b22c83","tid":2272542,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EVpsnWiU0AIl1kA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEVpsnWiU0AIl1kA.jpg&h=51015644&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96055e9a15e8a912fdced897a06da2b76767b6c4","tid":2272542,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8Jm6yL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8Jm6yL.jpg&h=b40b748c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63011111d83fcb1fc4654a8d3e0d529e25bdedfd","tid":2272542,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:36:46.000Z","msg":"好似大長今瘟疫個段<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c95c945c6f18175334b7f790e133711033de5b8","tid":2272542,"uid":267791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"他收到的消息是很多人不是因為武漢肺炎病死，而是餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16d0c8642878082e853538be87d2e2e9703a208","tid":2272542,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"宜家用幾星期埋地雷，之後用幾十年清地雷"},{"pid":"901f9c60652b6f33dfbb0caa99276fa1a5e9dd5a","tid":2272542,"uid":239086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c16d0c8642878082e853538be87d2e2e9703a208","tid":2272542,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"宜家用幾星期埋地雷，之後用幾十年清地雷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:49:16.000Z","msg":"唔清啦，脫北下場都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}